{% comment %}
  Organization Schema for SEO - Company Information
  Updated: 2026-05-29 - v5
  Schema Type: Organization (valid for all properties)

  aggregateRating was REMOVED: a site-wide, self-serving rating on the
  Organization violates Google's review-snippet guidelines (ratings about
  the business as a whole) and risks a structured-data manual action.
  Ratings belong only on Product schema where real, verifiable reviews
  exist (see snippets/product-rich-schema.liquid, which emits ratings only
  when product.metafields.reviews.* is present).
{% endcomment %}

